    "To open the settings window without the menu bar item, search for \"BrightIntosh Settings\" in the the macOS %@ Spotlight search." : {
      "comment" : "Spotlight Search and Launchpad reference macOS features. Use the term that is common or used by Apple in each of the languages for this feature.",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um das Einstellungsfenster ohne das Menüleisten-Element zu öffnen, starte BrightIntosh einfach über das Launchpad neu. Alternativ kannst du nach \"BrightIntosh Einstellungen\" in der macOS %@ Spotlight-Suche suchen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To open the settings window without the menu bar item simply restart BrightIntosh from the Launchpad. Alternatively, search for \"BrightIntosh Settings\" in the macOS %@ Spotlight search."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para abrir la ventana de configuraciones sin el elemento de la barra de menú, simplemente reinicia BrightIntosh desde el Launchpad. Alternativamente, busca \"Configuraciones de BrightIntosh\" en la búsqueda de Spotlight de macOS %@."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pour ouvrir la fenêtre des paramètres sans utiliser l'élément de la barre de menu, redémarrez simplement BrightIntosh depuis le Launchpad. Alternativement, recherchez \"Paramètres BrightIntosh\" dans la recherche Spotlight de macOS %@."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Per aprire le impostazioni senza il bottone nella barra del menù riavvia BrightIntosh dal Launchpad; altrimenti cerca \"Impostazioni di BrightIntosh\" nello Spotlight %@ di MacOS."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "メニューバーのアイコンを使わずに設定画面を開くには、既にBrightIntoshを開いた状態でLaunchpadから起動してください。また、Spotlightから”BrightIntoshの設定”を検索することもできます。"
          }
        },
        "pt-PT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Para abrir a janela das definições sem o item da barra de menu, simplesmente reinicie o BrightIntosh a partir do Launchpad. Alternativamente, procure por \"Configurações do BrightIntosh\" na pesquisa Spotlight do macOS %@."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "要打开不包含菜单栏项的设置窗口，只需从启动台重启 BrightIntosh 即可。或者，在 macOS %@ Spotlight 搜索中搜索“BrightIntosh 设置”。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "若要開啟不含功能表列選項的設定窗口，只需從啟動台重新啟動 BrightIntosh 即可。或者，在 macOS %@ Spotlight 搜尋中搜尋「BrightIntosh 設定」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
